<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Account Deletion Warning</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #fff5f5;}
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(200,0,0,.09);}
        .header { background: #e53935; color: #fff; padding: 28px 20px; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { padding: 36px 22px; }
        .footer { background: #f9f9f9; color: #888; text-align: center; font-size: 13px; padding: 18px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .btn { background: #e53935; color: #fff; padding: 12px 30px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; margin-top: 20px; display: inline-block;}
        .highlight { color: #c62828; font-weight: bold;}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Account Deletion Scheduled</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <strong>${userName}</strong>,</p>
            <p>Your account at <strong>${companyName}</strong> is scheduled for deletion on <b>${deleteDate}</b>.</p>
            <p>If you wish to keep your account, please click the button below:</p>
            <a class="btn" href="${reactivationLink}">Keep My Account</a>
            <p style="margin-top:25px">If you do not act before <span class="highlight">${deleteDate}</span>, your account and all data will be permanently deleted.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            If you did not request this, please <a href="${supportLink}">contact support</a> immediately.<br>
            &copy; 2025 ${companyName}
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
